  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study is to compare the safety and efficacy of pulmonary vein isolation using the
      endoscopic ablation system in comparison to irrigated radiofrequency current ablation in
      patients with drug-refractory persistent atrial fibrillation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
